}  and @fsux{nindiŋir} priestesses in their @fsux{ŋipar} shrines. Before @wDN{Enlil}, within the @wTN{E-kur}, before @wDN{Nanna}, within the @wTN{E-kiš-nu-ŋal}, the …… shall speak their prayers.””


@(26-29=c3119.26) @q[,]{“@q[,]{“And as for you, 
